::Kaiser/*******::
       "Yes of course sir.  Come along Synergy.  It's time to visit Sir 
Flashy Dot."  He leads the way out of the base and through the woods to where 
the unknown bot is standing.  "Why hello there Sir Flashy Dot, how may we, 
the Tripredacus, be of service?"

       The unknown bot just cocks his head to one side curious as to what the 
crazy old coot was talking about.
